    // rate_limit_middleware = std::make_shared<middleware::RateLimitMiddleware>(100, std::chrono::seconds(60)); // 100 requests per minute
    ```
-   **Distributed Rate Limiting:** For multiple application instances, Redis can be used to store and synchronize rate limiting counters.

